message.zh_TW: 我覺得你做的沒錯。\.最好不要跟這種危險的事情有任何關係。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]

text.en_US: You have to wonder how they would be able to grow the bamboo so densely...
text.pt_BR: Como ser que eles conseguem cultivar tantos bambus?
text.ko_KR: 대나무가 어떻게 저렇게 밀집하게 자라는 게 가능한지 생각해볼 필요가 있어...<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]
text.zh_CN: 不知道他们是怎么把竹子种得这么密的...<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]
text.ja_JP:
運営がどうやってこんなにみっちり
竹を育てられたのか、
不思議に思うべきだよ...<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]
text.de_DE: Ich frag mich, wie die es schaffen, den Bambus so dicht beieinander wachsen zu lassen...
text.zh_TW: 不知道他們是怎麼把竹子種得這麼密的...<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]

text.en_US: Maybe that's what the giant shoots around here are for.
text.pt_BR: Talvez seja pra isso que esses brotos gigantes esto aqui.
text.ko_KR: 그래서 저 거대한 새싹이 여기 있는 건가 봐.<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]
text.zh_CN: 也许就是那些竹笋长出来的吧。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]
text.ja_JP:
もしかしたらそれは、
このあたりにある
大きなタケノコのせいかもね。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]
text.de_DE: Vielleicht gibt es deswegen hier überall diese riesigen Sprösslinge.
text.zh_TW: 也許就是那些竹筍長出來的吧。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]

text.en_US: They grow into a ton of bamboo stalks!
text.pt_BR: Eles crescem em uma tonelada de caules de bambu!
text.ko_KR: 저게 다 대나무 줄기로 자라는 거지!<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]
text.zh_CN: 一堆竹笋长出一丛竹子！<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]
text.ja_JP:
タケノコは大量の竹に
成長するんだよ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]
text.zh_TW: 一堆竹筍長出一叢竹子！<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]

text.en_US: Then they make more shoots, and it creates a whole forest almost instantly!
text.pt_BR: Ento eles fazem mais brotos, e isso cria uma floresta inteira quase instantaneamente!
text.ko_KR: 그런 다음 자란 줄기가 또 새싹을 만들고, 결국 이 숲 전체가 되는 거야!<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]
text.zh_CN: 然后竹子再长竹笋，生生不息！<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]
text.ja_JP:
そこからもっとタケノコを増やして、
すごいスピードで森ひとつ
作っちゃうんだ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]
text.de_DE: Die dann noch mehr Sprösslinge verteilen, und im Nu hast du nen Bambuswald!
text.zh_TW: 然後竹子再長竹筍，生生不息！<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]

text.en_US: ... I was going to suggest someone out there just really likes gardening.
text.pt_BR: ... Eu ia sugerir que algum por aqui realmente gosta de jardinagem.
text.ko_KR: ... 난 그냥 누군가가 정원 가꾸는 걸 되게 좋아하는 건 줄 알았는데.<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]
text.zh_CN: ...我猜估计是设计师很喜欢园林吧。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]
text.ja_JP:
...単に、ガーデニングが大好きな人が
いるのかもねって話をしようと
しただけなんだけど。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]
text.de_DE: ... Eigentlich wollte ich damit nur sagen, dass da wohl jemand wirklich gerne gärtnert.
text.zh_TW: ...我猜估計是設計師很喜歡園林吧。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/01/10]
